{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"28":"Foods (Kitab Al-At'imah)"},"section_detail":{"28":{"hadithnumber_first":3736,"hadithnumber_last":3854,"arabicnumber_first":3736,"arabicnumber_last":3854}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3834,"arabicnumber":3834,"text":"حدثنا واصل بن عبد الاعلى، حدثنا ابن فضيل، عن ابي اسحاق، عن جبلة بن سحيم، عن ابن عمر، قال نهى رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم عن الاقران الا ان تستاذن اصحابك","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":28,"hadith":99}}]}